# Strict Dependency Versions

Use exact versions in Node manifests. Avoid ranges such as `^`, `~`, `*`, or `x`.

## Examples

```
# BAD
"typescript": "^5.4.0"
"vite": "~5.0.0"

# GOOD
"typescript": "5.4.0"
"vite": "5.0.0"
```
